title: Estonia Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Estonia increased 28 percent in October of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Estonia averaged 4.91 percent from 1995 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 28 percent in October of 2022 and a record low of -6.80 percent in December of 2009. This page provides the latest reported value for - Estonia Food Inflation - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Statistics Estonia
